Balanced Program


Check Capital Management's Balanced Program complements its equity programs.  For many investors, especially those who are retired, incorporating the stability of bonds is important.  Bonds can provide dependable cashflow for purposes ranging from living expenses to funding a child's or grandchild's college education.
In addition to the bonds, and similar to Equity-Income Program accounts, covered call option positions may be employed.   Balanced Program Portfolios are tailored for each individual. 
   














