Check Capital Management Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. It primarily provides its services to individuals, typically high net worth individuals. The firm also provides its services to investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm invests in growth stocks of large cap companies. It also invests in fixed income securities including taxable, tax-free, or corporate bonds. The firm employs fundamental ...
Check Capital Management Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. It primarily provides its services to individuals, typically high net worth individuals. The firm also provides its services to investment companies, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, and corporations. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. The firm invests in growth stocks of large cap companies. It also invests in fixed income securities including taxable, tax-free, or corporate bonds. The firm employs fundamental and quantitative analysis to make investments. It benchmarks its investments against the S&P 500 Index. The firm employs a combination of in-house and external research for its investments. Check Capital Management Inc. was founded in 1987 and is based in Costa Mesa, California with additional offices in Santa Monica, California and San Marcos, California.
